snippet.title: ARTIFICIAL - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
ARTIFICIAL is a physics-based first-person puzzle platformer developed by Ondrej Angelovic. Players will pick up and throw objects, sneak around enemies, and manipulate physics-based mechanisms to survive in the underground colony. ARTIFICIAL is launching in February 2024 for PC.
